text: Pultenaea sp. Genowlan Point is a critically endangered undescribed species of flowering plant in the family Fabaceae–Faboideae. It is only known from one population at Genowlan Point () in the Capertee Valley within the Rylstone local government area of New South Wales. ==References== Genowlan Point Category:Flora of New South Wales Category:Undescribed plant species
title: Pultenaea sp. Genowlan Point
